USERINFO_DESCRIPTION: Using this command will open an embed listing various stats of a user's Sofi account. You can also select a different language by using the dropdown menu at the bottom
UI_SLASH_DESC: Choose a user you want to inspect
LANG_CHANGE_SUCCESS:
Your language has been successfully changed to **{{language}}**! Please note that our translation update is still in early phases of development and doesn't yet cover all of our existing commands!

Untranslated commands include:

- **Deck**
- **Stats**
- **Event**

If you find any missing text, faulty translation or broken embeds and functions while using this language, we encourage you to report these issues by using the command `{{prefix}}lrt <Input>`. Alternatively, you can report your findings on our [Official Support Server](<https://discord.gg/sofi>)!
